echnique during the next decade in parallel the swedish group developed the whole pancreas transplantation technique with enteric diversion it was the onset of the whole pancreas reign the enthusiasm for the technique was rather moderated in its early phase due to the rapid development of liver transplantation and the need for sharing vascular structures between both organs liver and pancreas during the modern era of immunosuppression the whole pancreas transplantation technique with enteric diversion became the gold standard… for spk pak pta cs maint uses authors parameter link    angela cullen eva von schaper  fresenius agrees to buy app for up to  billion bloomberg news archived from the original on  retrieved    the discovers on the key patents were np desai soonshiong pa sandford mw grinstaff and ks suslick adding k s wong to the two  patents see further readingcitation needed  crowe deborah  october  celgene closes abraxis acquisition los angeles business journal retrieved  october  subscription required  company overview of nanthealth llc bloomberg businessweek  february  retrieved  february    shawn baldwin september   dr patrick soon shiong generates billions of value creation in medicine fast company   dolan brian sep   soonshiong’s big rollup gets a name nantworks retrieved  january    mcbride ryan  october  biotech billionaire’s supercomputer cuts cancer analysis to  seconds fiercebiotechitcom retrieved  february    tirrell meg  cancer researcherturnedbillionaire starts new company bloombergcom retrieved    rival drug firms team up to test new cancer treatment approach stat  retrieved    baker peter  if cancer becomes biden’s cause a bold but polarizing doctor is on call the new york times issn  retrieved    soonshiong patrick sep   message from the ceo and president retrieved  april  selfpublished source  crow patrick  soonshiong pattrick  patrick soonshiong talks with asus michal crow about the imminent hopedfor healthcare revolution cs maint uses auth